            "answer_text": "I can tell you the importance of hiatorical monuments in India as following-.1.These are the important and visual source of analyzing the history of India, very precisly.2. These monuments represent the style of Indian Art and Culture.3.In India there are lots of monuments connected with the religious feelings.A.Sanchi Stupa-Its a Budhhism based monument,so u can undrstand here about some budhhist mindset.B.Khujraho Temples-Hindu and Bhudhha both religious feelings being poured here.C.Meenkashi Temple-It is located there at Madurai,Which is a very nice piece of Art.D.Swarn Mandir-In Amritsar,here u can feel the sentiments of Sikhism,it is built by Guru ArjunDeva.E.Ajmer Dargah-Muslim sentiments being poured here.4.Historical monuments also playing an important role in business of India.Foreign and Indian visitors have to pay for visiting some monumetns which comes under ASI..Lastly i say that it is very important to visit them all but also preserve them for our future genration. ",
